<div class="date_column">DATE</div>

<div class="content_column">FEATURED EVENT <span style="float:right;padding-right:8px"><a href="/Connect/Calendar-of-Events" style="color:#ffffff"><img src="/Portals/_default/Skins/SiteSkin/images/plus.jpg" /></a></span></div>
